{"tid":943270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[網絡孤兒] 女露胸男裸下體　泰國年輕人新時尚網傳","createTime":"2018-12-16T12:14:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T13:29:31.000Z","uid":122,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fa88d235fc6b55e1279d4e44e114440546228c73","tid":943270,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T12:14:29.000Z","msg":"泰國社交網路上，近日吹起一陣裸露風，不但有年輕女子在知名景區露乳拍照，還有不少青少年裸體與自己的機車合影，他們都把照片上傳網路與網友分享，引起一陣譁然！<br />\n<br />\n根據泰國《新泰日報》報導，近日有1組大尺度性感寫真照，在網路上流傳，照片中是1位染金髮年輕女孩，步行在太古普吉老城區街道以及多處著名景點附近，有時是露胸，有時則是露出內衣，大膽在公眾面前公開拍照。<br />\n<br />\n另外，也有一群青少年與年輕男子，公開裸體與自己的機車合照，然後上傳網路分享，看起來像某些年輕群體中的一種大膽潮流。<br />\n<br />\n有些泰國網友認為，這種裸露風氣，會影響青少年的價值觀，呼籲網路監管部門介入調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181216/640_752eb116499f771a9ad27a53b8553aa2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181216%2F640_752eb116499f771a9ad27a53b8553aa2.jpg&h=b1f4a6ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181216/640_aaaf36d07fca79d8a6d84e34eefd283f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181216%2F640_aaaf36d07fca79d8a6d84e34eefd283f.jpg&h=5c410aae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbcba0e67d086d9c926f5a52b9023728c4469800","tid":943270,"uid":46943,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T12:15:35.000Z","msg":"賓周呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6745af224b3509bc3bcce6229366bd13d25ccf71","tid":943270,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T12:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/08/064026_07fe8d602176b374e707c4419b5c72cb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F08%2F064026_07fe8d602176b374e707c4419b5c72cb.png&h=e2fd55ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65f58c